-- China May Bar Developers From Evicting People From Homes to be Demolished
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-12-16T00:18:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-16/china-may-bar-developers-from-evicting-people-from-homes-to-be-demolished.html
China may bar property developers
from evicting residents from homes scheduled for demolition,
according to revised draft rules for housing compensation on the
government website yesterday.  The rules may also ban the use of violence in kicking out
residents, the statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
